name: 2016 Olio Quattrociocchi Biologica
description: Produced exclusively from organic olives grown on the Quattrociocchi Estate, this extra virgin olive oil is medium-intense in fruitiness with a powerful and strong aroma, characterized by vegetal notes, green grass, mint and rosemary. Its taste is fine and balanced with a flavor of garden vegetables and dried fruit with a strong, pungent finish.
